SUMMARY:Fire Ecology
DESCRIPTION:Fires are important part of many of North Carolina’s ecosystems.  Learn about the important role of fires and how they promote the growth of many plants in our state and beyond in this virtual program. \nThis virtual program is especially for kids in grades K-8\, but everyone is welcome.  You do not need to join ecoEXPLORE before the program\, but should you choose to create an account for your child so they can get started documenting wildlife for scientists and earning prizes\, visit ecoexplore.net. \nRegister here
URL:https://naturalsciences.org/calendar/event/fire-ecology/
LOCATION:Virtual\, NC\, United States
CATEGORIES:Children,Citizen Science,K-12 Students,Virtual
ORGANIZER;CN="ecoEXPLORE%20Team":MAILTO:ecoexplore@naturalsciences.org
END:VEVENT
