SUMMARY:Make a Carnivorous Plant
DESCRIPTION:North Carolina is home to many amazing meat-eating plants! Join ecoEXPLORE Central to learn all about carnivorous plants before making your own paper pitcher plant. \nThis virtual program is especially for kids in grades K-8\, but everyone is welcome.  You do not need to join ecoEXPLORE before the program\, but should you choose to create an account for your child so they can get started documenting wildlife for scientists and earning prizes\, visit ecoexplore.net. \nRegister here
URL:https://naturalsciences.org/calendar/event/make-a-carnivorous-plant/
LOCATION:Virtual\, NC\, United States
CATEGORIES:Children,Citizen Science,K-12 Students,Virtual
ORGANIZER;CN="ecoEXPLORE%20Team":MAILTO:ecoexplore@naturalsciences.org
END:VEVENT
